{"tid":1049713,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[睇樓主打機] 鋼鐵雄心4 --- 捷克斯洛伐克","createTime":"2019-03-06T12:59:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T17:02:34.000Z","uid":52200,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"935281732d0b4a763c98388e0c424dd11e20905d","tid":1049713,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T12:59:15.000Z","msg":"背景：<br />\n係第一次世界大戰之後，本身係多民族國家嘅奧匈帝國戰敗分裂。根據民族自決原則，捷克斯洛伐克獲得獨立，並且成為中歐唯一民主國家。<br />\n<br />\n立國後短短20年，就要面對納粹主義國家威脅。與納粹德國接壤嘅蘇德台地區，因為以日耳曼人為主體，受到希特勒鼓動，繼以發生脫離捷克並與德國合併之危機，迫使捷克對德國的重要防線拱手相讓。與此同時，西方國家(英、法)，卻繞過捷克，與德國簽訂慕尼黑協定，企圖以捷克利益換取歐洲和平。<br />\n<br />\n究竟，面對極權主義威脅，以及西方左膠嘅背叛，捷克是否必需割地求和？中歐唯一的民主國家能否堅持到曙光出現？戰後，又能否成為抵抗共產主義的堡壘？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXbM7un.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXbM7un.png&h=2585ba30&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d00ddf7953b877b68ea2852d0d3886273ee897e","tid":1049713,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ChDYDT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ChDYDT.png&h=a00f52e2&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FMgQPLz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFMgQPLz.png&h=32218d34&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pB8GWqz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpB8GWqz.png&h=734ba00a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一開波嘅時候，距離大戰仲有兩年時間，希望可以進一步發展工業。"},{"pid":"0b7bb56cc3a2f80a1e9b090662a6d45cf07c89b7","tid":1049713,"uid":188155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:09:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24dbbadafc13c584f9d18a211a370192c59167a6","tid":1049713,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:09:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5GD39L4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5GD39L4.png&h=e882a418&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n眾將士開往前線佈防。"},{"pid":"85753bf5a3a44fc8a1aebeff1f1a97eee2987ec1","tid":1049713,"uid":34791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:13:50.000Z","msg":"捷克太易玩了<br />\n求民主盧森堡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7324ff78102577392ec69c09aca0cc0b2a93d6a7","tid":1049713,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85753bf5a3a44fc8a1aebeff1f1a97eee2987ec1","tid":1049713,"uid":34791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:13:50.000Z","msg":"捷克太易玩了<br />\n求民主盧森堡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:16:28.000Z","msg":"開左iron mode，冇save大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，錯一步都會收皮。<br />\n額外目標：完成munich disagreement achievement (佔領Munich)"},{"pid":"38ce8c2f9238152bf167d3540b8a99ad4c2e87fc","tid":1049713,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:29:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gg8GWwY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgg8GWwY.png&h=da86d27f&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A4of0YE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA4of0YE.png&h=068d3b66&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n出於防禦戰略需要，延續一戰的壕溝戰術，希望可以抵擋希魔嘅裝甲師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc744bd07bcd5bfca9f18558662dc95bab3f7496","tid":1049713,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:39:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PjoS3eX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPjoS3eX.png&h=93ed96dc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1936年年尾，國家工業化進程基本完成，人民生活質素大幅提高，捷克 與 斯洛伐克 之間的國族分裂問題舒緩，國民開始願意參軍(recruitable population +0.50%)，保衛家園的準備亦要開始了。"},{"pid":"aa14555489a8f91c24651a47fd5f18a0a62b8de1","tid":1049713,"uid":52200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T14:22:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0qqieAi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0qqieAi.png&h=41625bb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XSMmcmZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXSMmcmZ.png&h=eea7697d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1937年中日爆發全面戰爭，亂世之中，守護自由民主並非靠唱吟&quot;今天我&quot;，捷克陸軍進行第一次軍事改革，所有步兵師配置工兵連、反坦克連，並加在全國大徽兵規模。"},{"pid":"c0960950e11b1b52936c8b90fbe07f66b9dea6b0","tid":1049713,"uid":76419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T14:54:48.000Z","msg":"其實玩一舖要幾耐想買好耐 但驚無時間玩咁耐<br />\n所以我依加通常玩day of infamy 玩幾個字就完"},{"pid":"c41d7bb63939ed1ffa2fcaee96e4d5f28b3c9f95","tid":1049713,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0960950e11b1b52936c8b90fbe07f66b9dea6b0","tid":1049713,"uid":76419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T14:54:48.000Z","msg":"其實玩一舖要幾耐想買好耐 但驚無時間玩咁耐<br />\n所以我依加通常玩day of infamy 玩幾個字就完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T15:06:20.000Z","msg":"一鋪一個月左右 (大概40幾個鐘)"},{"pid":"599912cc0b36e7301608379032893d3ecffa468f","tid":1049713,"uid":52200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T15:16:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yB0FtcJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyB0FtcJ.png&h=b90e772d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1938年，係國家社會主義鼓動下，奧地利已經與德國合併，加上匈牙利，捷克已經有4分3的國境被納粹主義包圍，情況岌岌可危。此時，在敵我邊界中，每一塊領土只有1-2個師的兵力守護。雖然蘇德台地區有堅實防線，但對匈牙利邊界的守備力量十分薄弱，防線一擊即破。"},{"pid":"577634b4293aecafd657cc2f7e4ec884d82eb561","tid":1049713,"uid":44391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T18:50:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b9ff48b9e1f395820f38916e999464ee1268564","tid":1049713,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T19:02:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6439ed574864b7fb5a26b10499a7df6af1ea3148","tid":1049713,"uid":52474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T17:02:34.000Z","msg":"無了？"}]}